programme.desc: Encik Fadzlan mengugut Fariz untuk menceraikan Ain. Hingga akhirnya Fariz terpaksa juga menceraikan Ain. Fariz kecewa dengan sikap ayah dan ibunya. Setelah bercerai,Ain mula berubah sikap dan kemurungan. Apakah Fariz akan kembali rujuk pada Ain?

programme.title: Rindu Yang Terlarang
programme.desc: Tokwan mula susah hati dengan keadaan Ain yang semakin kemurungan. Fariz cuba untuk rujuk semula dengan Ain. Sementara itu, Ilah dan Adnan cuba untuk menyatukan Ain dengan lelaki lain. Apakah Ain akan menerimanya? Berjayakah Fariz rujuk semula dengan Ain?

programme.title: Rindu Yang Terlarang
programme.desc: Ilah menghalau Ain dari rumah atas apa yang Ain lakukan. Fariz hadir memujuk semula Ain di rumah. Malangnya, Ain menghalau Fariz dan meminta Fariz pergi. Tok Wan dan Ain akhirnya membuat keputusan untuk berpindah dan membina hidup baru. Fariz tetap mencari Ain? Adakah mereka akan bersatu?

programme.title: Rindu Yang Terlarang
programme.desc: Fariz mengikuti gerak geri Tokwan dan mencari Ain hingga di kedai. Ain berpura-pura tidak mengenali Fariz. Dalam diam, Ain terluka dan terlalu merindui Fariz. Sementara itu, Fadzlan dan Rohana merancang untuk menyatukan Fariz bersama Rania yang turut sama memendam perasaan pada Fariz. Apakah Fariz akan bersetuju?

programme.title: Rindu Yang Terlarang
programme.desc: Rohana desak Fariz agar berkahwin dengan Rania. Bagaimanapun Fariz menolaknya dan bertegas walau apa cara sekalipun, dia akan tetap berkahwin dengan Ainnura. Dalam waktu yang sama, dalam usaha untuk mendapatkan nombor telefon Ainnura, Fariz sanggup ke pejabat Ainnura, bagaimanapun Iqram tidak setuju kerana bimbang rahsia Ainnura adalah bekas isteri Fariz akan terbongkar. Dalam waktu yang sama, Ilah berusaha dengan pelbagai cara agar Ainnura tidak rapat dengan Fariz.

programme.title: Cubit - Cubit Cinta

programme.title: Striker Hati Ayah

programme.title: Rat Race
programme.desc: A Las Vegas casino magnate, determined to find a new avenue for wagering, sets up a race for money.

programme.title: Blindfire
programme.desc: A police officer who while responding to a violent hostage call, kills the African American suspect only to later learn of his innocence. Sensing this was a set-up, and facing repercussions, he must track down the person responsible while examining his own accountability and the ingrained racism which brought him to this point.

programme.title: Mister Mayfair - A Song To Kill For
programme.desc: Max Mayfair has it all; a beautiful girlfriend, Ava, a new London crime family, and thanks to his latest heist, a priceless diamond necklace. However, when mafioso Calbones henchmen catch up with Mike and Armen, determined to drag them back to New York to pay for their crimes, Max has everything to lose. Teaming up with his old friend, Marseille Mafia crime boss, Paul, Max hatches a plan to lure the New York Mafia to Mayfair.

programme.title: Mojave Diamonds
programme.desc: A former MMA fighter and his brothers must rescue their kidnapped family from a dangerous crime syndicate after $50M of illegal diamonds gets stolen.

programme.title: Broadcast
programme.desc: After a billionaire creates a drug called INOC which stops the aging process, the future of a world where death no longer exists is seen. The story of the fate of mankind is told while also revealing an elusive truth to its unknowing spectator.

programme.title: Come Out Fighting
programme.desc: During WWII, the American army have raced their way through the countryside on the border of France entering Nazi Germany. Hitler has deployed his secret weapon. Lieutenant Frank Ross encounters the Nazi weapon and an intense aerial battle ensues.

programme.title: Mister Mayfair - The Spyce Of Life
programme.desc: Returning from a romantic getaway with Ava, Max finds himself on the wrong side of the law yet again. Now blackmailed by MI6, Max must spy on two suspected terrorists; Aziz and Omar, who are regular customers at his club. Accompanied by his London crime family, Max breaks into Omars country estate and discovers his sinister plan. With everything on the line, Max must race to uncover a highly skilled hackers identity before its too late.

programme.title: Broken Star
programme.desc: Abandoned by her friends and family and with her career in jeopardy, starlet Markey Marlowe is sequestered in a duplex with a reclusive landlord who just may be more dangerous than she is.

programme.title: Pocket Listing
programme.desc: Double crosses, adultery, murder, mistaken identity, and revenge ensue when a mysterious power player and his sultry wife hire a disgraced Los Angeles property broker to discreetly market and sell their Malibu villa.

programme.title: Any Bullet Will Do
programme.desc: Two Brothers find themselves on opposing sides of the fight as one hopes to help abolish slavery while the other believes it is his God-given right.

programme.title: American Sicario
programme.desc: Based on the true story, Edgar Valdez, drug lord and cartel leader, is betrayed by one of the brothers. Seeking retribution, Valdez will risk it all to gain control of the Feliz cartel.

programme.title: Centigrade
programme.desc: A married couple find themselves trapped in their frozen vehicle after a blizzard and struggle to survive amid plunging temperatures and unforeseen obstacles.

programme.title: Johnny And Clyde
programme.desc: Johnny and Clyde are two serial killers who are on an endless crime spree. They decide to assemble a group of criminals and misfits to steal from Alanas casino and pull off the heist of the century.

programme.title: High Voltage
programme.desc: After a lightning strike kills the lead singer of a band, she is resurrected with electrifying special abilities.

programme.title: Operation Sea Wolf
programme.desc: The German Navy and the last remaining U-Boats, were formed together for one last mission to attack the United States Homeland.

programme.title: Chosen
programme.desc: The Jews of Eastern Europe are being massacred by the thousands. Galvanised into action after the death of his wife, Hungarian barrister Sonson finds himself leading an inspirational fight back against the increasingly desperate and dangerous Nazis.

programme.title: Hideout
programme.desc: Evading police at a remote farmhouse after fumbling a robbery, four criminals discover that the family living there is not who they appear to be.

programme.title: The Legion
programme.desc: Noreno, a half-Roman, is entrusted with the mission of crossing the snowy mountains of Armenia, swarming with Parthian patrols, to seek help for his slowly dying men.

programme.title: Blood Of Redemption
programme.desc: When the most powerful criminal empire in the land comes crumbling down from within, it is up to a former henchman to put the puzzle pieces together in order to find those responsible and extract revenge.

The Great Pyramids are reduced to pile of rubble as black funnels snake across the desert. Its disaster, Code Yellow, as the "storm on steroids" is only just beginning to rend the earth.

programme.title: DAY 2
programme.desc: J.T. wakes up to another unsettling coincidence. The car delivered to his home as a "loaner" while his damaged truck is being repaired is a green Jeep Cherokee, just like the one in the file. Unnerved, J.T. decides to take the day off to investigate further. After discussing the list of suspects with Sikorski, he asks his physician friend Dan to test the blood on the bullet found in the briefcase. He asks his buddy Tim Sanders, publisher of the local paper, to have his staff examine the crime scene photo for signs of tampering and to check the papers files for information on Roy Bremmer. He asks his brother-in-law Brad, a professor of material sciences, to examine the mysterious briefcase.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E101
programme.desc: Para decidir quien comprar las yeguas, Florencia reta a Victoria a una carrera por el llano donde la ganadora se quedar con los animales; Victoria acepta el desafo. Una inesperada visita de Hilario asusta a Federico, mientras que Fernanda no se amilana y le recuerda a su medio hermano que Victoria es quien lo est dejando en la ruina; Hilario le asegura a Fernanda que no permitir que su propia hija lo despoje de lo que le pertenece. En medio de la carrera, Florencia desenfunda su arma y dispara al viento para obligar a Victoria a detenerse; esta ltima se extraa al ver a la seora Del Casal armada, dispuesta a matar, pero Florencia es incapaz de seguir su plan, por lo que decide terminar la carrera. Frente a un confundido Nicols, Victoria irrumpe en la hacienda Los Samanes para exigirle a Florencia una explicacion sobre el por que esta cavo una fosa cerca del lugar donde disparo durante la carrera: debido a que Florencia niega su participacion en la excavacion, Victoria arremete en contra de ella para que confiese su intencion de asesinarla.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E102 - Episodio 102
programme.desc: Tras descubrir a Nicols besando a Florencia, Victoria le reprocha a su amado el dejarse manipular por su esposa, quien se escuda detrs de la memoria de su padre para dar lstima. Por ms que Nicols se niega a creer que Victoria sea capaz de asesinar a un caballo, Florencia lo convence de que su amada Guanipa es capaz de todo por recuperar su amor; en ese momento, dos peones de la hacienda le informan a la pareja que la casa del difunto Rosendo Zapata est en llamas. A Cantarrana llega un enfurecido Nicols en busca de una explicacion sobre lo sucedido, a lo que Victoria sin dejarlo hablar- asegura haber sido ella la culpable. Cada la noche, Victoria le reclama a su padre el haber asesinado a General y el haberlo marcado con el hierro de ella para que la inculparan, pero Hilario le asegura que el no es culpable de esa muerte; Victoria est dispuesta a esclarecer el asunto. En un nuevo da, Florencia se encuentra con Moncho en un lugar apartado de la hacienda para entregarle una cierta cantidad de dinero por haberla ayudado a matar al caballo de su padre; Moncho est convencido de que alguien ms est detrs de la idea de matar al animal.

programme.title: Wardens - S03:E01 - Operation Grizzly Bear
programme.desc: This week, wardens are tackling a situation involving a missing child that was reportedly pulled away by a bear... Luckily, its just a training drill. At the same time, shed antler hunting season kicks off, keeping the wardens busy!

programme.title: Backcountry Rescue - S01:E01 - Rookie Pressure
programme.desc: Anthony strives to prove himself as medical lead responding to a snowmobile crash on Togwotee Pass.

programme.title: The New Frontier - S01:E05 - The Planet Makers
programme.desc: From the beginnings of our Solar System four and half billion years ago there remains tantalizing clues to its evolution; remnent debris: asteroids and comets. They vary in size from grains of dust to mountain sides, footballs to planetoids. They were the building Now within our grasp these rocks of ice and dust are ready to give up their secrets.

programme.title: Hollywood Weapons - S03:E05 - Getting to Know Rick OShea
programme.desc: In this episode we get know Larrys friend Rick OShea (Ricochet). Terry and Larry test several different films where bullets are manipulated in order to get an amazing result. They test scenes from Skyfall, Suicide Squad, American Ultra, and The Bear.

programme.title: Hollywood Weapons - S03:E06 - We Hear Ya!
programme.desc: Larry and Terry test several requests from viewers. They will test a bunch of crazy scenes from Bad Boys 2, Under Siege, A License to Kill, and Bangkok Dangerous.

programme.title: Jim Shockeys Uncharted - S01:E10 - The Ancient Ones
programme.desc: Arctic. Jim and Coreys Arctic adventure starts with Muskox, an animal practically forgotten since pre-historic times in the Arctic.

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E18 - The Queen Mother An Affectionate Tribute
programme.desc: The Queen Mother, who lived as long as the century itself, was a beloved figure in British life. She was a symbol of bravery during the Second World War and a timeless icon of steadiness, winning a deep affection from people that was only matched by the Queen herself.

programme.title: Dropped - S02:E05 - Saddle Sores
programme.desc: The guys are feeling great as they leave sheep territory, but the 22-hour trip to Tom-Tom, the first moose camp, feels endless. Itll take them two long days of riding to get there. As they head into moose land with a successful sheep packed up high, trouble always seems just around the corner on their journey. After riding for eight hours, issues start cropping up.

programme.title: Dropped - S02:E06 - Church on the Mountain
programme.desc: In the Yukon, decisions can change everything in a heartbeat, especially in such a tough landscape. The brothers are closing in on the enormous mountain grizzly, now just 500 yards away, and its up to Chris to make the call.

programme.title: Dropped - S02:E07 - Valley of Snow
programme.desc: The Keefer brothers are stuck at Church Camp as the snow keeps pounding down, and they can barely see anything. Theyre snowed in and dont know when theyll be able to continue their hunting trip. Theyre starting to face a bunch of problems.
